{
  "stem": "14190.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was petrified.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was clutching the ball.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I-- I went out of this ditch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was silent there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there was no kids.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was no-- none.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Nothing was happening.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It-- debris everywhere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was awful scene.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was awful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then I hear from far my father's voice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Bachia, Bachia, Bachia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then, I felt somebody grab me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that was my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he dragged me out of there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Carry me out of there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Later, we found out that most of the kids that were there, they were-- they were no more.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They were killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And that was my introduction to-- to-- to war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Very soon after, our windows were covered with-- with all sorts of things so the light will not go through.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then my father talked about the-- that we need to go to bankers to find places, you know, in case of alarm.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He was instructing us what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And what they were trying-- they were-- they started to do preparations with food, with-- have enough bread, have enough water.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I knew that things are-- awful things are about to happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And sure enough, not long after this, my father and I were standing on the street and watching German soldiers marching through the-- in the middle of the street.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They were so impressive, I tell you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And scary-looking, though, but very impressive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They were marching with a goose step and then singing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know the song?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember the song.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh my goodness, 'The Happy Wanderer,' to the tune of 'Happy Wanderer.'",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whenever I hear now the song, that's what it reminds me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I cannot listen to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It makes me absolutely-- I-- I just can't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was still playing the song.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were marching.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
